Package com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.transform.row

Provides classes which are used to modify data tables by row.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ContextDataRow<C>
    The ContextDataRow is a data row associated with a particular "context." Basically, this interface allows a data row to be a simple container holding some informational object which can be accessed.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicDataRowsRemoval
    The BasicDataRowsRemoval is a row-removal data table transformation which only uses the row's data to determine if it should be removed or not.
    BasicRowWiseColumnTransformation<T>
    The RowWiseColumnTransformation is a row-wise data table transformation which modifies a single column via a specified function.
    CompositeRowWiseDataTableTransformation<R extends RowWiseDataTableTransformation>
    The CompositeRowWiseDataTableTransformation class provides a simple structure for combining multiple row-wise data table transformations into a single row-wise transformation.
    ContextlessRowWiseColumnTransformation<T>
    The ContextlessRowWiseColumnTransformation is a row-wise column data table transformation whose transformation function is based purely on the initial value of the column.
    ContextualRowWiseColumnTransformation<T,C>
    The ContextualRowWiseColumnTransformation is a row-wise contextual data table transformation which transforms a single column in the table.
    ContextualRowWiseTransformation<C>
    The ContextualRowWiseTransformation class is a row-wise data table transformation which provides structured access to some extra "contextual" information when performing transformations.
    DataRowsRemoval<C>
    The DataRowsRemoval class is a mutating data table transformation which removes rows from the table.
    DegenerateContextDataRow
    The DegenerateContextDataRow class provides a simple context data row which holds itself as a context.
    FunctionRowWiseColumnTransformation<T,C>
    The FunctionRowWiseColumnTransformation is a contextual row-wise column transformation where the transformed values are calculated via a function acting on the initial value of the column and the data row being transformed.
    RowWiseDataTableTransformation
    The RowWiseDataTableTransformation class is used to construct row-wise mutating data table transformations.
